Name: Bunny Count
About the game: Bunny Count is a First Person Stuffed Animal Doll Shooter featuring classic game types in a cartoony , story book type setting. Capture The Flag , Team Deathmatch and Kill Confirmed are included as online and offline game modes! Its the Bunnies VS The Bears ! Who are you gonna be? Works great for Local Area Networks and Parties! See you on the Bunnyfield!!!! This game is being produced, developed by Crypto Sports Games , Platinum Crypto.
